</para>
<para id="element-20"> <term>Solution : </term> Let 
<m:math> 
<m:msub>
<m:mi> θ </m:mi>
<m:mn> 1 </m:mn>
</m:msub>
</m:math> 
and 
<m:math> 
<m:msub>
<m:mi> θ </m:mi>
<m:mn> 2 </m:mn>
</m:msub>
</m:math> 
 be the angles for first and second pairs of cross products. Then,
</para>
<para id="element-21">
<m:math display="block">
